w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/BGWMC-Save-Our-Venue.-Credit-PRESS-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/BGWMC-Save-Our-Venue.-Credit-PRESS-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/BGWMC-Save-Our-Venue.-Credit-PRESS-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/BGWMC-Save-Our-Venue.-Credit-PRESS-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>伦敦东部的Bethnal Green Working男子俱乐部已推出了“战斗基金”众筹以拯救场地。</p><p>该空间一直是各种音乐，喜剧和戏剧演出的主持人，多年来一直举办过众多的开创性表演。包容性的建筑已上市，并拥有合法证书 - 承认该二手级是官方的歌舞表演剧院。但是，这些保护措施不足以使场地免于受到威胁。</p><p>由Bethnal Green Working Men&#39;s Club（FOBGWMC）的朋友（由当地人，表演者，下注者，程序员和工会成员组成的社区团体）创建，“战斗基金”将有助于付费，以说服塔尔塔小村庄委员会拯救俱乐部。 </p><figure id="attachment_3841618" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841618" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841618" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/BGWMC-Save-Our-Venue.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="BGWMC-保存我们的场地。信用：出版" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/BGWMC-Save-Our-Venue.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/BGWMC-Save-Our-Venue.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/BGWMC-Save-Our-Venue.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/BGWMC-Save-Our-Venue.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/BGWMC-Save-Our-Venue.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/BGWMC-Save-Our-Venue.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841618" class="wp-caption-text"> BGWMC  - 保存我们的场地。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>该基金需要在4月8日之前筹集12,000英镑，该基金将支付全面的特许调查和建筑物估值，以及计划申请成本，这将使至关重要<br />建筑物的保护。</p><p>该基金还拥有18,000英镑的扩展目标，这将使FOBGWMC能够制定有财务预测的强大商业计划，并支付所有咨询和会计师费用。</p><p>每个向该基金捐款的人都有机会赢得BGWMC商品的奖励，包括艺术家劳伦斯品牌的A3俱乐部印刷品，以捐款超过70英镑，BGWMC啤酒垫捐款超过30英镑，以及Save BGWMC广告系列的捐款，以超过20英镑的捐款。</p><p>您可以访问<a href="http://www.crowdfunder.co.uk/p/save-bgwmc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>捐赠。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DDNGIMbIfdu/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.