le-to-smile-again-following-partial-facial-paralysis-3415171">公开谈论他的健康斗争</a>。这包括在他因“疾病” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-postpones-north-american-tour-dates-due-to-illness-ive-done-everything-to-get-better-3242083">取消了北美“正义”之旅的开场时间</a>后，在2022年透露了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-reveals-facial-paralysis-from-ramsay-hunt-syndrome-3244867">他在拉姆齐·亨特综合症的诊断</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="贾斯汀·比伯（Justin Bieber） - “对不起” |歌曲故事" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/B0urWO2u994?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>除了对他的健康状况的评论外，还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-appears-to-be-back-in-the-studio-3830135">报道说比伯又回到了录音室</a>，并计划很快卷土重来。当新年开始时在工作室里看到他时，这些都得到了加剧，当<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-is-working-on-new-music-with-mk-gee-3790800">MK.Gee透露他一直在与新材料合作时</a>。</p><p>如果工作室的输出作为完整专辑汇集在一起​​，那将是他自2021年“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/justin-bieber-justice-review-2900928">正义</a>”以来的第一个录音室发行。</p><p>贾斯汀·比伯（Justin Bieber）在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-raps-about-being-high-in-new-video-after-denying-drug-use-3841579">在新视频中，贾斯汀·比伯（Justin Bieber）在新视频中说“高”</a> 。</p> ;
